ualized roofing system may vary. Your final quote will be provided after inspection at no obligation.</p><table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td align="center" style="padding-bottom:32px;"><a href="https://api.leadconnectorhq.com/widget/booking/gG1ruFfEWkUXO7eIB8NR" style="display:inline-block;background:#B8935A;color:#09090A;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;padding:16px 32px;border-radius:4px;">Schedule Your Free Consultation</a></td></tr></table><div style="border-top:1px solid #E7E0D2;padding-top:24px;"><p style="font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:13px;color:#2A2A2A;margin:0 0 4px;">Andrew</p><p style="font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:13px;color:#2A2A2A;margin:0 0 2px;">Metroplex Metal Roofs</p><p style="font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:13px;color:#2A2A2A;margin:0;">(817) 382-3338</p></div></td></tr><tr><td style="background:#FFFFFF;padding:20px 32px;text-align:center;"><p style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#57534E;margin:0;">© 2025 Metroplex Metal Roofs · Dallas-Fort Worth, TX</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>`;
